doctype html
html(lang='ru')
  +head('../','VIDEO 18')
  link(rel="stylesheet", href="../css/ekko-lightbox.css")
  body
    +header("../")
    main
      +slider('../')
      .container.videos
        .row.mx-auto
          .col
            h3 VIDEO 18
            h4 MMA. Kara Teller vs Darya Balina and Tais.  May, 2012
            p.
              The first match is between the experienced fighter <b>Kara Teller</b> (Moscow,  5’7” / 119 lb) and the newcomer <b>Darya Balina</b> (St. Petersburg,  5’4” / 124 lb). Almost the whole fight is fought standing up where Kara clearly dominates. Darya turns out to be very strong and holds out for nearly two rounds.
            img.mainImg(src='../img/videos/18/main.jpg' alt='main')
            p.
              The second fight (Kara Teller vs Tais), unlike the first one, consists of mainly mat wrestling. For two rounds Tais struggles to win the fight with a chokehold or submission lock, occasionally taking hits from her opponent. The final result is quite surprising.
            h5 <u>ММА</u> Darya Balina vs Kara Teller 
            a.btn.btn-primary.screensBtn(data-toggle='collapse' href='#collapseExample' role='button' aria-expanded='false' aria-controls='collapseExample')
              | SCREENSHOTS
            #collapseExample.collapse
              .col-md-12.text-center
                  .row.justify-content-center
                    - var n = 0;
                    while n < 15
                      - n = n+1
                      a.col-sm-4(href='../img/videos/18/mma-sportivnyj-prazdnik-2012-1/'+n+'.jpg' data-toggle='lightbox' data-gallery='example-gallery')
                        img.img-fluid(src='../img/videos/18/mma-sportivnyj-prazdnik-2012-1/'+n+'.jpg')
            h5 <u>ММА</u> Kara Teller vs Tais
